esolution. However, it is also shown that these advantages\ncome with the cost of increased side lobes. Both the simulated and the measured\nresults demonstrate the superiority of the proposed uniform sparse array design\ncompared to classical fully populated uniform arrays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Oct 2022 21:15:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-24"}
