m describing the semi-infinite system. Moreover, we\ndemonstrate that damped topological waves may be studied within the framework\nof modal superposition by utilizing the damped modal spectrum to characterize\nthe variation topological wave group velocity and predict edge-to-bulk\ntransitions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2022 01:30:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2023 00:32:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-25"}
