\nhosted by ellipticals. The radio jets show no preferential alignment with the\nminor axis of the galactic bulge or disk, apart from a possible mild tendency\nfor alignment among the most disk-dominated systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2022 04:29:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-11"}
