{ar}^d$ and to underline that despite of their simple algebraic\nstructure Archimedean copulas may exhibit surprisingly singular behavior in the\nsense of irregularity of their conditional distribution functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2022 10:42:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-24"}
