SE\nestimates may need to be corrected as a function of the geochemical\nincompatibility of these elements. Alternatively, if RLE are indeed in\nchondritic relative proportions in the BSE, accretion scenarios that are\nefficient in affecting the BSE chemical composition should be questioned.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2022 11:49:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-07"}
